|------|--------|
| `scripts/reset-admin.js` | Created ÔÇö resets admin to `admin123`, sets `mustChangePassword: false` |
| `data/db.json` | Updated via script ÔÇö new password hash for admin |
| `server.js` | Fixed `proto` detection, added [LOGIN:1-7] verbose logging, changed `sameSite` to `'lax'` |
| `public/index.html` | `doLogin()` now shows actual `r.error` from server |

### How to verify
1. Restart the server: `node server.js`
2. Open the app URL in browser
3. Log in with `admin` / `admin123`
4. Server console should show `[LOGIN:7] OK user="admin" role=admin`

